---

This project was inspired by and references the protocol shape of
Anthropic's `claude-desktop-buddy` reference implementation
(https://github.com/anthropics/claude-desktop-buddy, MIT-licensed).
The BLE Nordic UART + heartbeat-JSON wire protocol used here follows
that project's conventions so a Paper running this firmware can, in
principle, also accept frames from any compatible desktop bridge.

The bundled CJK font at `data/cjk.ttf` is GenSenRounded Regular,
originally distributed with the M5Stack `M5EPD` library's examples.
It is redistributed here for convenience; its own license terms apply.
